We've got to destroy it, or we'll never make it to Wayne Manor.

5
01:04:05.380 --> 01:04:06.430 
蝙蝠爸爸
Uh... Bat-Dad?

6
01:04:06.630 --> 01:04:08.000 
我觉得你应该看看这个
I really think you should see this.

7
01:04:08.170 --> 01:04:09.630 
例行检查
Building survey!

8
01:04:10.430 --> 01:04:12.100 
这座楼可不够安全
This building's not up to code!

9
01:04:18.940 --> 01:04:20.780 
抓住了
Gotcha.

